38
00:03:32,618 --> 00:03:34,618
Kami sudah beritahu kamu yang kami bukannya penyihir!

39
00:03:35,618 --> 00:03:38,718
"Akira Mafune (26)" -Ya, memang betul kami menaiki FD putih

40
00:03:38,718 --> 00:03:40,118
