43
00:03:47,018 --> 00:03:51,218
Ya, kami mahu pergi memancing ikan bass hitam di Tasik Fuyuna.

44
00:03:51,218 --> 00:03:53,318
Jadi? Adakah ia benar

45
00:03:53,318 --> 00:03:56,818
